  <brief_title>A Comparison of Volatile Anesthesia and Total Intravenous Anesthesia (TIVA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of Volatile Anesthesia and Total Intravenous Anesthesia (TIVA) on Ecchymosis, Edema, and Intraoperative Bleeding in Rhinoplasty</official_title>
